brigitte nielsen ( born gitte nielsen ; 15 july 1963 ) is a naturalised - italian , danish - born actress , model , singer and reality television personality who began her career modelling for greg gorman and helmut newton and several years later acted in the 1985 films red sonja and rocky iv.

seeing red at the movies : brigitte nielsen was the title character in this 1985 sword & sorcery saga

